        <abstract>
            <p>Discusses phases of climate.</p>
            <p>Describes fossil mammals discovered by Auguste Bravard in South America.</p> 
<p>Has had argument with Bishop of Oxford [Samuel Wilberforce] about CD’s book [<hi rend="italic">Origin</hi>].</p>  
<p>Discusses review in <hi rend="italic">Annals and Magazine of Natural History</hi>. Guesses that T. V. Wollaston is the author.</p> 
            <p>Discusses evidence of shells on Madeira.</p> 
<p>Comments on paper by Wallace ["On the zoological geography of the Malay Archipelago", <hi rend="italic">J. Proc. Linn. Soc. Lond. (Zool.)</hi> 4 (1860): 172–84].</p> 
        </abstract>
